room_title: Escape room "Motel Room 13" by Sherlock's Escape Rooms in Florence (KY)
room_address: 40 Martha Layne Collins Blvd. Cold Spring, KY 41076
room_description: You’ve been traveling for quite some time and now you’re looking for a place to rest. There’s an old motel on the roadside with the vacancy sign dimly blinking. The desk clerk hands you the key to the last room left – Room 13. No one has stayed in there for quite some time, though…at least not since that one night.
